    {
      "type": "text", "id": "selector_text", "x": 610, "y": 577,
      "width": 380, "height": 96,
      "text": "Selector SP v11 场景分类器\n4步判定: ID_000预判 → 上下文辅助 → 特殊规则 → 互斥锚定\n输出: 13个场景ID (ID_001~ID_013) + ID_000兜底\n⚠ 命中率 60-70%（目标 ≥85%）",
      "originalText": "Selector SP v11 场景分类器\n4步判定: ID_000预判 → 上下文辅助 → 特殊规则 → 互斥锚定\n输出: 13个场景ID (ID_001~ID_013) + ID_000兜底\n⚠ 命中率 60-70%（目标 ≥85%）",
      "fontSize": 13, "fontFamily": 3, "textAlign": "center", "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "strokeColor": "#374151", "backgroundColor": "transparent",
